OL,3,CSecond murder charge after body found
OL,4,Cfollowing garage fire
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Ffollowing the discovery of a body
OL,8,Fafter a garage fire.
OL,10,FOn Thursday 26 February, West Mercia
OL,11,Fpolice officers attended a report of a
OL,12,Fgarage on fire on Surman Street. A man
OL,13,Fwas found dead inside.
OL,15,FDavid Jones, 34, of no fixed address,
OL,16,Fhas today been charged with murder.
OL,18,FHe is due to appear at Kidderminster
OL,19,FMagistrates Court tomorrow.
