OL,3,CSecond murder charge after body found
OL,4,Cfollowing garage fire
OL,6,FOn the 9 March, Thomas Bowen, 34, of
OL,7,Fno fixed abode, was also charged in
OL,8,Fconnection with the murder and remains
OL,9,Fon remand.
